{"tid":1312283,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[正能量] 整咗條片，希望中立嘅人睇完會明白，同時為各位同學打打氣！","createTime":"2019-07-13T13:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T15:17:26.000Z","uid":278775,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4d46d733e6cb22857a3587d46937539c9a8c20e6","tid":1312283,"uid":278775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">啱啱開錯台</span><br />\n我相信有唔少同學最近都好嬲、好頹同好累<br />\n我都係，但各位同學千祈唔好放棄<br />\n抗爭從來都係長時間嘅<br />\n我知道你會累，你會痛，你會怕<br />\n<strong>但記住！<br />\n累 先會令你堅強<br />\n痛 先會令你成長<br />\n怕 先會令你勇敢</strong><br />\n<br />\n由雨傘運動到逃犯條例，再到信用系統<br />\n如果大家都覺得係有問題嘅<br />\n請盡快為自己嘅未來發聲<br />\n唔好好似片入面嘅我咁<br />\n去到最後先黎後悔就太遲啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位黃同學加油！<br />\n香港加油！不撤不散！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4ru-q_maV08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4ru-q_maV08&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=7d23b5b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4ru-q_maV08</a>"},{"pid":"1b9372ee50ea7f8936234af4174fffcab484b4c9","tid":1312283,"uid":278775,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"推比更多人睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28c9210866a70bc2feda262d682ff34a65e964d","tid":1312283,"uid":278775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cada73ed7d7f6ef493b4a0e5aabf2b48f3ca294b","tid":1312283,"uid":62210,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"依幅圖..<img src=\"/assets/fa